behaviortree

Interface StandardNode

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, Node, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    StandardNodeImpl

    public interface StandardNode
extends Node
    A representation of the model object 'Standard Node'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Traceability Status
    • Operator
    • Label
    • Component Ref
    • Behavior Ref
    • Traceability Link
    • Leaf
    • Parent

    See Also:
    BehaviortreePackage.getStandardNode()
